civics.name: Wage Framework
civics.description: Every hour, every member of the government gets a wage according to the index wage. The senate can adjust this index wage by changing the custom stat on the White-Tiger citizen. Wages are paid out of the personal wealth of the White-Tiger citizen so the Government has to make sure to keep this wealth stocked up. Owed wages are tracked. The starting index wage is 60$ per hour.
